---
title: Sticky Sweet-Soy Beef Rump Tacos with Asian Slaw & Garlic-Sriracha Aioli
description: Sometimes it can be tricky to find new ways to jazz up tacos but not tonight - a sticky honey-soy glaze on beef is taking out the guesswork and creating new inspiration for your taco night. We also threw a garlicky sriracha aioli into the mix for a bit of fun.

*We’ve replaced the pea-pods and spring onions in this recipe with cucumber due to local ingredient availability. It may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*
